{
  "stem": "14737.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I go to the-- to the pharmacy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The pharmacist was, by the name of Ilkovitch, Joseph, a very nice man, a charitable man, a smart man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ask him, what is it he overhead in the pharmacy came in, and people?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said to him the following, listen, let's clarify this here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll find here a man who's going to go next town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And let him talk to someone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let him see what happened there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he takes a neighbor there, a non-Jew, sends them-- listen, you go to [NON-ENGLISH], about half an hour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You come back, and report, and tell us what happened there-- what?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he goes there and finds out the Jews were taken away, taken to the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from the train, they took them away further.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the Jews-- not even a single wasn't left in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had a population of at least 60, 80 families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And where were they taken?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we know that from [NON-ENGLISH] it could be only one direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Could go only to Beregszasz-- a small, small train is going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It couldn't be different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they probably took them to-- to-- to that direction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, there's nothing-- no place else can they go from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took them by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If they would take them through Dovhoje, then they goes a different direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it's true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now this pharmacist, a nice man-- what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They take us to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They take us too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I say to him, I have an idea what to do something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, there are communicable diseases all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was from time to time typhoid here, I know the doctor here, a non-Jew by the name of Batory.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
